<resources>
    <!-- Android 12+ (API 31) Material You Dynamic Colors -->
    <!--
        This app intentionally does NOT use Material You dynamic colors.
        The Windows 11 Fluent Design Dark theme is a core part of the app's
        visual identity, with a carefully chosen color palette (#202020 background,
        #0078D4 accent, #60CDFF light accent). Applying dynamic colors would
        override these choices and break the consistent Fluent Design look.

        If dynamic color support is desired in the future, it can be enabled
        per-component using DynamicColors.applyToActivityIfAvailable() or
        by creating a DynamicColors theme overlay here.
    -->
</resources>
